{"tid":1438962,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我知道大家已經好攰","createTime":"2019-08-10T03:05:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T04:36:14.000Z","uid":182637,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"858c2a34dbba451fb841748b55e37d22979118de","tid":1438962,"uid":182637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:05:01.000Z","msg":"由6月到宜家 我知大家已經開始攰<br />\n逢星期六日都出黎遊行<br />\n<br />\n去到呢一步 我見到呢個運動步緊五年前既後塵<br />\n宜家每日4:00既毅進記招就好似之前既4:00許sir咁<br />\n<br />\n拎方仲賢單野黎講 我地係收左班毅進仔皮<br />\n我係facebook instagram都見到大量恥笑佢地既post <br />\n反而小左推遊行 推五大訴求 推新聞 推被捕人士既post<br />\n<br />\n宜家政府想爭取中立人士既支持 所以開始分化我地 會用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">部分使用暴力人士</span></span></strong></span>去分化和理非同勇武派<br />\n<br />\n雖則每一次出完黎遊行食完復活蛋我地都會進步一次<br />\n但同樣地 藍絲都識進步<br />\n<br />\n我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔可以因為方仲賢單野收左佢地一次皮就無限打飛機</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地要好好重整下隊伍 繼續作戰</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n要宣揚三大紀律 八項原則<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NF9adui.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNF9adui.png&h=0a2f8cac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">兄弟爬山 各有各做<br />\n不割蓆 不分化 不篤灰</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 希望睇到呢個post既和理非 唔好同前線割蓆 <br />\n係機場加油接機 為香港人發聲"},{"pid":"624fb139c6f39a790756ebee89b5997d6901d54d","tid":1438962,"uid":182637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:06:05.000Z","msg":"我自推一下"},{"pid":"863a366798af6b8343dcdc977320438ae42447ff","tid":1438962,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:06:26.000Z","msg":"大埔機場見"},{"pid":"cff027997c3d136ae9e9dbb275c6e84918943af4","tid":1438962,"uid":261544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:07:44.000Z","msg":"推，<br />\n從來無諗過割蓆，<br />\n知道大家都好累，心理壓力好大<br />\n<br />\n但要記得呢個係長期戰爭<br />\n我地輸左，香港整個未來都會輸"},{"pid":"4487f5e4c65506ff7b7f1416ad293d7bb9a57223","tid":1438962,"uid":182637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:10:59.000Z","msg":"我知道仲有好多人睇cctvb 好多中立都會中招 信左林奠 <br />\n我地要係文宣個到著手"},{"pid":"52a8cba4ec8e763718b19f019edfadf4c7b14201","tid":1438962,"uid":182637,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:11:41.000Z","msg":"我又自推一下"},{"pid":"13cecbbe53de25d340088fe37fbac30f704b5f33","tid":1438962,"uid":205972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:17:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"31bfcecfa480964df7dae753244cc2f2e52048b7","tid":1438962,"uid":50414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:18:24.000Z","msg":"希望大家繼續努力"},{"pid":"9efcde28605e90085ad456249cb0276075900024","tid":1438962,"uid":182637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T03:32:59.000Z","msg":"不割蓆 推<br />\n2:00大埔呀香港人"},{"pid":"875a5f7296985961900fd4f16307b0993e726044","tid":1438962,"uid":182637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T04:36:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}